name: Videl - Dragon Ball Z
description:
Videl from Dragon Ball Z

This one has several different variants of her.

V2 Usage

Use Videl, pigtails for her pigtail version (not twintails).

Use Saiyawoman separately for best results.

This can be used with lower Cfg / Weight for more aesthetic, Higher Cfg/Weight for closer to anime style. Having Cfg of 7-7.5 with weight of 0.7-0.8 is what gave me these kinds of results

V1 Usage

For example, if you want short hair videl, just use "Videl".

For her twintails version, Just use "twintails"

For Saiyawoman, use "saiyawoman"

Include "biker shorts" for twintails and Videl versions for better resulsts

Do not include "Videl" for her other variants for best results.

This version does not include her Dragon Ball Super version. I may include in a different version.

Use 0.8-1 weight.

Please comment, like, and share your gens! :)

modelVersions.name: v2.0
modelVersions.description:
Better overall accuracy, works with Videl + Pigtails in the same prompt

Can use with lower weights and retain accuracy for more style, higher weights for closer style to the anime
